data.description: MOVIATED SELLERS!  Offering $2500.00 at Closing for interest rate buy down or Closing Costs.  This Great 3-Bedroom 2 Bath Home with 2 Car Garage w/ Ceiling Storage.  Located in the heart of the Estates of Seven Hills in Spring Hill.  Less than hour from Tampa International Airport.  The YMCA is part of the Community charm,  and its active culture is great for the whole family and staying active.  Only 2.3 miles to Tampa General Hospital of Spring Hill,  minutes away from Shopping.  The homes backyard is perimeter is complete with PVC fence installed in 2022.  The fence is complete with 2 6ft wide gates opening on either side.  The backyard has shaded trees to allow everybody and the pets to play during the Florida summer time heat.  Great wide open space for cookouts and entertainment.  The Home has a New Asphalt Shingle Roof and 360 degree gutters installed in 2022. The 10 year warranty is 100% transferable to the New Homeowner at Closing.  New matching Stainless Appliances in Kitchen and Laundry room.  All Appliances are WI compatible.  The Modern Rustic theme Kitchen is complete with a large Farm sink and all shaker grey cabinets and drawers have soft closings hinges.  No slamming ever!  The Beautiful Quartz counter tips were installed in 2021.  The Waterproof Luxury Vinyl Flooring the kitchen is installed under all the cabinets and through the hallway and in the laundry room.  The oversized living room is complete with vaulted ceiling and matching farmhouse light chandlers though out the home  the interior is tastefully accented with real barnwood,  adding to the small country attraction of Spring Hill living.  The inside air handler and outside heat pump air conditioner units were replaced in 2021.  ALLOWING THE NEW OWNER TO MOVE IN WORRY FREE!.  Call to make your appointment today!
